{
  "stem": "2578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because around, I would say, in March of 1945, when the weather started to be warmer, and I realized that, by being in this camp, I will drop because of the conditions and the ration that we got-- because we only got a little bit of soup a day-- I decided, with the last of my ability, that I will have to go out of the camp and do some work in order to get an extra portion of soup.",
      "word_count": 80
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I was finally-- after being refused once-- I finally got the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the OK from the German who was-- from the-- from the doctor who was in charge of the camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he let me go out to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The work that I did was actually ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because there were two groups of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were digging holes in the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In those days, the-- the-- the ground was still frozen and we had to cut it with those picks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- we made these holes, and another group came, and they filled it up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we would advance to another area, a few hundred feet, to dig another hole.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they got finished filling up the previous hole, they will come over to ours and fill up this one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we would, among our-- the inmates, among themselves, would talk about it, and we would laugh-- to a certain degree-- that, what are we doing?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Evidently, we are doing only in order for the-- for the SS who were watching us-- for them to have an excuse to have this kind of duty.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tell me, who was this camp doctor that--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a Hungarian Jewish inmate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a-- an inmate, just like the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
